    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827240/extras/0c4196220e9ea382cd4448d270c5bb5c.avif?t=1765201161\" width=636 height=244 /></span><br>对轻松获利的渴望将一支小型雇佣兵队伍和雇主引导到了一个在森林中迷失的领地，受到神秘疾病的折磨。这可能是黑死病在整个中世纪欧洲传播的新种类，也可能是当地女巫的阴谋。一个狡猾的商人试图利用这场悲剧谋取个人利益，将雇佣兵困在危险的游戏中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827240/extras/3df654c68626b67107a569a1a39b1110.avif?t=1765201161\" width=614 height=200 /></span><br><br>《瘟疫领主》游戏的序幕将为您介绍核心机制，并为在瘟疫领主中等待着您的冒险做好准备。<br><br>与受感染者战斗，探索被神秘流行病笼罩的土地，并尝试揭示其秘密！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827240/extras/b58fdafd2ddbc4f5fd90376bdd608e72.poster.avif?t=1765201161\" width=614 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827240/extras/b58fdafd2ddbc4f5fd90376bdd608e72.webm?t=1765201161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827240/extras/b58fdafd2ddbc4f5fd90376bdd608e72.mp4?t=1765201161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 特色 </h2></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827240/extras/b82a588823ad19d0069fc39ebd612317.webp?t=1765201161\" width=615 height=20 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 探索五个主要游戏城市之一。<br></li><li> 指挥一支小型训练有素的士兵小队。<br></li><li> 建立自己的军事营地，包括设有防御工事和制作结构。<br></li><li> 利用技能和建筑进行主游戏中的三个基本工艺之一。<br></li><li> 构建、制作和应用陷阱、路障和防御工事。<br></li><li> 体验由经验丰富且装备精良的小队组成的强大武器库。</li></ul>",
